title: Satin Edge 2 Sided Ingrown Toenail Lifter, 8.0 Ounce
description: Satin edge 2 sided ingrown toenail lifter, flat end aids in lifting and applying antiseptic underneath toenail. Helps tend to painful ingrown toenails. Curved end gently lifts toenail.

title: Opi Correct & Clean Up Refillable Corrector Pen 4ml

Including the pen plus one replacement tip OPI Correct & Clean Up Refillable Corrector Pen comes in a handy refillable correct and clean up pen for professional application every time. Directions of use: ?Dab along cuticles to remove traces of nail lacquer. ?Wipe tip on tissue to clean. ?Refill pen by pulling tip out and refill through tip hole with an OPI Polish Remover
